metadata.name: even the decorations are
metadata.description:
just as they were in your room."



When Jia's mother heard what they said, she looked at Jia Cong with a confused face as if she had returned to her own room. Is it true that the grandson was deliberately prepared to please himself?



Cong brother, what is this...?



Jia Cong laughed and said, "Old lady, this used to be Grandma Lai's room. She decorated these facilities after you. I don't think they are too bad.



Jia Mu just nodded, did not speak, sat down in the head.
